content.name: UCS_XTSources_DCOInternal
content.desc: This program demonstrates using an external 32kHz crystal to supply ACLK, and using a high speed crystal or resonator to supply SMCLK. MLCK for the CPU is supplied by the internal DCO. The 32kHz crystal connects between pins Xin and Xout. The high frequency crystal or resonator connects between pins XT2IN and XT2OUT. The DCO clock is generated internally and calibrated from the 32kHz crystal.
